<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Acesso à Internet Restrito</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root { --primary-color: #667eea; --danger-color: #ff6b6b; --success-color: #25D366; }
    body { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; padding: 20px; }
    .card { border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); backdrop-filter: blur(20px); background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95); }
    .card-header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b 0%, #ee5a52 100%); color: white; border: none; padding: 2rem; }
    .wa { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #25D366 0%, #20c997 100%); color: #fff; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
    .logo { height: 50px; border-radius: 8px; }
    .info-card, .payment-card, .steps-card { background: #f8f9fa; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .btn-copy { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); border: none; color: white; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="main-container" style="max-width: 800px;">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header text-center">
        <div class="status-icon mx-auto" style="width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <i class="bi bi-wifi-off" style="font-size: 2rem;"></i>
        </div>
        <h1 class="brand mb-3">Acesso à Internet Restrito</h1>
        <div class="badge bg-danger rounded-pill px-3 py-2">Acesso Suspenso</div>
        <% if (logoPath) { %><img class="logo mt-3" src="<%= logoPath %>" alt="Logo Geniesoft" /><% } %>
      </div>

      <div class="card-body p-4">
        <div class="info-card">
          <h5>Olá, <strong><%= customerName %></strong>!</h5>
          <p class="text-muted mb-0">Seu acesso à internet está atualmente restrito. Isso pode ocorrer por um dos seguintes motivos:</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card">
          <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0">
            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-credit-card text-danger me-2"></i>Fatura pendente ou vencida.</li>
            <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-calendar-x text-warning me-2"></i>Seu período de serviço expirou.</li>
            <li><i class="bi bi-gear text-info me-2"></i>Restrição temporária pelo sistema.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-card text-center">
          <h6><i class="bi bi-headset text-success me-2"></i>Fale com o Suporte</h6>
          <p>Para resolver, entre em contato com nosso administrador pelo WhatsApp.</p>
          <a class="wa" href="https://wa.me/<%= adminWA %>?text=Olá, minha conexão foi suspensa. Usuário: <%= customerName %>." target="_blank">
            <i class="bi bi-whatsapp"></i> Chamar no WhatsApp (<%= adminDisplay %>)
          </a>
        </div>

        <% if (paymentAccounts && (paymentAccounts.bank_transfer || paymentAccounts.cash)) { %>
          <div class="steps-card">
            <h6><i class="bi bi-credit-card me-2"></i>Opções de Pagamento</h6>
            <div class="row g-3">
              <% if (paymentAccounts.bank_transfer) { %>
                <div class="col-md-6"><div class="payment-card"><h6>Transferência Bancária</h6><p class="mb-1"><strong>Banco:</strong> <%= paymentAccounts.bank_transfer.bank_name %></p><p class="mb-1"><strong>Conta:</strong> <%= paymentAccounts.bank_transfer.account_number %></p><p><strong>Titular:</strong> <%= paymentAccounts.bank_transfer.account_name %></p></div></div>
              <% } %>
              <% if (paymentAccounts.cash) { %>
                <div class="col-md-6"><div class="payment-card"><h6>Pagamento em Dinheiro</h6><p class="mb-1"><strong>Endereço:</strong> <%= paymentAccounts.cash.office_address %></p><p><strong>Horário:</strong> <%= paymentAccounts.cash.office_hours %></p></div></div>
              <% } %>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="alert alert-warning">
          <strong>Importante:</strong> Após o pagamento, envie o comprovante ao admin para agilizar a reativação do seu serviço.
        </div>

        <footer class="text-center text-muted mt-4">&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Geniesoft - Seu Provedor de Confiança</footer>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
